snippet.title: The Dark Pictures Anthology: House of Ashes - Gameplay Reveal
snippet.description:
Trapped in a buried temple, unaware that something ancient and evil has awakened in the shadows…
Go deep underground in the first gameplay reveal of House of Ashes.
